    <tr><td><b>KnowAct-GUIClaw</b> (2026)</td><td>Personal GUI assistant with self-evolving memory and skill library on top of the OpenClaw framework.</td><td>Production-flavored instance of agents accumulating execution experience as reusable skill.</td><td><a href="https://huggingface.co/papers/2607.12625">HF</a> / <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2607.12625">PDF</a></td></tr>
